        <div class="flex gap-1 mb-4">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm text-primary" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">star</span>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm text-primary" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">star</span>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm text-primary" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">star</span>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm text-primary" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">star</span>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm text-primary" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">star</span>
        </div>
        <p class="font-handwritten text-xl text-on-surface leading-tight mb-4">"Super cute aesthetic! The spiral is actually sturdy and doesn't bend in my bag."</p>
        <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant/60">— Bianca R.</p>
      </div>
