        </div>
        <p class="font-handwritten text-xl text-on-surface leading-tight mb-4">"The best slam book replacement. Me and my friends are obsessed!"</p>
        <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant/60">— Sofia G.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-[#ffeefd] p-6 shadow-lg rotate-[4deg] hover:rotate-0 transition-all hover:-translate-y-2 cursor-default">
        <div class="flex gap-1 mb-4">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm text-[#7d4d5f]" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">star</span>
